  "descriptionShort": "Number of people using [improved sanitation facilities](#dod:improved-sanitation) that are not shared with other households, but where the facilities do not meet the criteria for safely managed sanitation.",
  "descriptionFromProducer": "Use of improved sanitation facilities not shared with other households, but not safely managed",
